        "subject": "Priority Consultation Booking",
        "html": "=<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #222; line-height: 1.6;\"> <h2>Hi {{$json.Name}},</h2> <p> Thank you for your interest and for taking the time to submit your inquiry. </p> <p> Based on the information you provided, we’ve marked your request as a <strong>priority inquiry</strong>. </p> <p> We’d love to discuss the best options available for you and answer any questions you may have. </p> <p> You can book a consultation at your preferred schedule using the button below: </p> <p style=\"margin: 30px 0;\"> <a href=\"https://calendly.com/jerohkylems/30min\" style=\" background-color: #000; color: #fff; padding: 14px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; \"> Book Your Consultation </a> </p> <p> We recommend reserving a slot as early as possible as availability may become limited. </p> <p> Looking forward to speaking with you soon. </p> <br> <p> Best regards,<br> Your Company Name </p> </div>",
